      "description": "Comprehensive reference guide for the Agentic Tool Kit (ATK) CLI and web app — covers every command, non-interactive flags for scripted/agent-driven use (publish, init, install, etc.), JSON output mode, core concepts (lockfile, tool adapters, trust levels, checksums), authentication, and troubleshooting. Use when the user asks how to do something in ATK, wants to know what a flag does, is debugging an ATK error, is authoring or publishing a new asset, asks Claude to publish/install/manage assets on their behalf, or needs clarification on ATK concepts like setup, sync, pin/freeze, or the org scope.",
